        "content": "\n**Gaps:**\n- `parse_posted_at`: ms-epoch vs sec-epoch branch, ISO8601 with/without `Z`, naive ISO (no tzinfo → should default UTC), empty/`None`, garbage string, negative epoch.\n- `Job.key` stability across mutated title/location.\n- `Job.content_hash`: same for identical title/location/url/department; changes when any one changes; does NOT change when `posted_at`/`salary_range` change (this is the whole point of the field — untested, easy to silently break).\n- `Job.to_row`: `raw` excluded, `key`/`content_hash` injected.\n\n```python\n",
